Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - Customer across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait - Customer when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - Customer in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait - Customer to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time between Accepted + Wait - Customer and the next occurrence of Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - Customer compared to the duration of Accepted + Wait - User in variants containing both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - Customer in variants that end with Completed + Resolved versus those that end with Completed + Closed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait - Customer when preceded by Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Minimum time it takes Accepted + Wait - Customer to be completed after Accepted + In Progress in cases that later execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Average cycle time of Accepted + Wait - Customer when the case includes at least one Completed + In Call activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time elapsed between the start of Accepted + Wait - Customer and the subsequent Completed + In Call, if any
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - Customer in variants that contain multiple waiting states (e.g., also Accepted + Wait - Vendor or Accepted + Wait - Implementation)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor occurs

Name: Total duration of Accepted + Wait - Customer in high-performance variants (top 10% by frequency) versus low-performance variants (bottom 10% by frequency)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - Customer when directly followed by Accepted + In Progress before any Completed + In Call occurs
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time from case start until Accepted + Wait - Customer is first executed in cases that eventually perform Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
